high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the coffee machine, then turn right to face the oven and look up at the microwave.
Take the potato out of the microwave and then close the microwave door.
Turn around and walk toward the wall, then turn right and walk up to the sink.
Put the potato in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and take out the clean potato.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the microwave.
Put the clean potato in the  microwave and close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the right, go straight then turn to the right and look at the microwave above the stove.
Open the microwave, pick up the potato inside, and close the microwave.
Turn around, go straight then right to face the sink to the right of the refrigerator.
Place the potato in the sink, run some water over it, and pick up the potato.
Turn to the right and go straight to face the microwave above the stove.
Place the potato inside of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Placed the rinsed potato in to the microwave.

high_descs: Take an egg out of the microwave
Wash the egg in the sink
Put the egg in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Wash an egg and place it back in a microwave
